Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:40.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, hurry up! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:47.11,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'm coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:53.10,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We have enough time, so don't be in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean that. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:56.45,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.59,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was sunny earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.45,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time wearing this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:04.17,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it to get dirty before we arrive at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:06.55,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,OK I see. Lets go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.79,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a drizzle. If we wait for a while, it's going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.77,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tomomi's fault because you were too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.57,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ok ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:38.28,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,My my, what ill mannered girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:50.52,eptitle,Eptitel,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEBE1D2&\pos(320,150)}Miracle Girls #25\NMysterious weather
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.82,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,You two, I feel guilty over your wasting the holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way. We really don't care about that. Right Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:01.19,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:05.41,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,When I came back I wanted to go travel with everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.85,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't because of my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.37,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,If you got well we could go as many times as we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:16.10,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,But could you apologize to Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.94,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I got in your way on such a wonderful day for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.06,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:25.59,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll go get some hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How come you didn't tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.09,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.14,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK, I'm pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:50.78,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But your flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.74,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:04:03.49,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK? Be careful, it's dangerous if you bump into someone on crutches, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.66,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And when you do secret talking, first all of you check around, and then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:14.07,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Secret talking? She means our telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.92,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you depressed? You can come here again after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:33.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but I think Kurashige senpai might feel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.46,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.79,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm frustrated because I can't do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:40.17,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, don't be so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.04,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go home in order to not get the dress wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:47.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:51.84,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh oh, it looks like rain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.13,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,If you hurry you won't be wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.26,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,See, you better run to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:01.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.41,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wait Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.97,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting on, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.13,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.42,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Meanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, why'd you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.07,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Because that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.10,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:38.88,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, hey Mikage. Haven't you finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:43.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You see I told Kagera I'd visit for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.93,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and you won't be in on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:50.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.73,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.61,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be that you were talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:58.51,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,There's only me and you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:02.04,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,or might you have been talking telepathically?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.84,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.33,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't make it because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.39,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga, if you could make it, what do you intend it to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.26,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,A.. terrific one..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.29,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.20,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you visit him tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No, I promised him I'd visit everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.47,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But the visiting hours will be finished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.37,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked you to wait here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.12,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.15,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, is anybody around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It looks alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:58.97,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.80,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're stepping on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, stepping on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.00,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well what are you doing just standing there then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:11.38,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.81,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the flower bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.95,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You're forgetting to say something, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.32,Default,Tomo&Mika,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:27.33,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:32.02,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well today's visiting hours are finished so go home with care and fix the flower bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.69,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You got it? How about the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.05,Default,Tomo&Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.10,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.67,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What is that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Did she see our teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way. If she did, she'd be very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,By the way... Do we have to give up even though we came to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:52.99,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.77,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.46,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.68,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's having an X-ray, so it's gonna take more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:08.40,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's impossible for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:14.13,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll have better luck tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.33,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that apron twit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah there's something strange about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:34.13,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We must've done something nasty to warrant a grudge like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.80,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, she seems to know about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:40.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:44.10,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You see, whenever we use telepathy, she's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way, you think too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:50.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The timing is always exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet her, it would rain afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.17,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:04.41,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, monster rainy woman. Next time I see her, she's going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.38,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, are you thinking seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Well, is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:22.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you think she'll sneak up on us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:29.21,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to take such an unscientific attitude. It won't be raining today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:31.32,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.59,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.06,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.83,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You really saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.67,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this gonna be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:56.02,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again, you're such a lifesavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.99,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You feel fresh after working hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:03.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.37,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,The sun in between showers is especially beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:12.85,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's the same as after a good sweat no crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.65,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.29,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if you've hung it all to dry, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:22.26,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Come on hurry up, or you'll be late for visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.40,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Great, it didn't get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Will you bring this one upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, you think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.46,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sorry, I had my sheet blown off by a strong wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.94,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Could you bring this one up also?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:03.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.67,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for sale
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for rent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.63,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:39.11,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That parrot is the mascot for children and seniors who are patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:43.38,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,If they knew he was gone, they'd be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.51,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What're we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.74,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Why don't you apologize with some excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.80,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise you guys can't come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.49,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:00.53,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,How come we can't come back here because of such a small problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.29,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Such a small problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:10.83,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}All right. It might be a small problem for you because you can go anywhere as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.85,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,But these patients cannot go out to find the parrot or buy another bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:23.88,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}I seem to remember your friend falling into this category. Now he can't go out as he likes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:32.60,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,When I came back I wanted to go travel with everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.17,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't because of my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, let's go apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:47.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go find the parrot. That woman can't go laying guilt trips on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.07,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.33,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be wonderful if you can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.95,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, but without your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:01.68,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'll do it for the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.02,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,She knows about us as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:17.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So why is she so nasty to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:21.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that nasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:24.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, I thought you were on my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:29.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it out on me. This thing happened because you dropped the sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:35.15,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, just watch it rain woman. Don't underestimate Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how can we find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:52.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, did you see a parrot like this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.39,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a green parrot around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.90,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.94,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kids, did you see a parrot like this big anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that parrot go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, I found a person who saw the parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:34.93,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:38.02,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,They said they saw a parrot in the forest over by the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:47.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi. Tomomi stop... I can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together. We've gotta find the parrot in a hurry or it's gonna be dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.67,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:57.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, wait here while I go explore a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:01.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What a bad day. I'll miss the visiting hours again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.05,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't meet senpai today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.81,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,If we find it you can meet him as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,How come we have to do such a stupid thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.42,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.57,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But, we promised her we won't use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.03,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.74,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:35.01,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,We promised without magic. Or can't you do it normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:42.95,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the easy way, at least you can run cheerfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.92,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget all you can do as a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.40,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,As a normal girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:19.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It flied this way right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:23.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi just wait. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,She's a rain woman after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a little concerned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, she's not nice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:41.45,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm referring to when she said to not forget all we can do as normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.49,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.94,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That woman always shows up whenever we use telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:51.78,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,If you bump into someone on crutches or the like, it's gonna be dangerous right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.29,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And when you do secret talking, don't forget to check first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:00.16,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two know what you're stepping on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.99,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I'm sorry. I had my sheet blown off by a strong wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:09.76,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Well that shows if we didn't use telepathy or teleportation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:13.47,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't bump into people or step on flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We can't catch him in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.41,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.47,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Cat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.01,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That parrot doesn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.84,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No it doesn't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:58.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a dangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:04.93,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,To the balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.74,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:14.52,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:16.77,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But we used magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.35,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:22.37,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that rain woman might be watching us and then show up to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.45,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all right because we could help the parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:36.42,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I know but I feel frustrated because we had to use power to find a parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:38.93,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.17,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:03.42,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You two found the parrot with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.36,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend and any patient can't go running out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:18.71,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,so spare a thought about those people if you get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we had better not use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:28.83,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}I didn't say that, because if you didn't have that power, this parrot wouldn't have been saved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:34.94,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem provided you only use your power for the proper occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.71,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.99,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I have a new bridge so it's time to go to a new town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.83,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.80,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Rain woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.71,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:38.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.80,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See you, Miracle girls. {Merry Poppins greets us ;p }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:55.06,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Parrot? In the hospital? I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have it or do you know a nurse who has a big apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.27,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Or somebody's attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:08.65,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}Well, I've never heard that before, and this hospital is all nursing so there's no attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.44,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,You might have a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.36,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.88,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:17.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.09,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, it must be our mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:26.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wow senpai isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:27.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.70,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Finally the rain has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.40,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it has, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who was that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:54.41,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage! I was scouted for volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.94,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,That's great Tomomi, I'm going to support you all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:00.39,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, if I accept that I'll transfer to a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.99,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.47,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll transfer to a different school!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:10.34,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:13.64,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:16.98,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:20.19,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:36.83,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:40.12,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:53.64,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:23:00.06,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:07.11,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.87,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.79,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:22.25,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:25.25,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
